					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13030130#post-4516147</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13030130/scp-5445#post-4516147</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2020 14:52:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Faraday Cage</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1856658</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't understand how customers are eating a skull.<br /> Humans don't have hyena teeth for crushing bone.</p> <p>This is what broke my suspension of disbelief.</p> <p>Possible fixes : Maybe something anomalous happens that makes it possible for a human to eat a skull.<br /> Or.<br /> Mention people are licking the blood off the skull surface and that's good enough for transmission, I guess, but still a bit silly.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
